content: Xiao Han is currently working at the PixelShiftas a computer vision algorithm intern. He just obtained his bachelor’s degree at the College of Information Science & Electronic Engineering (ISEE), Zhejiang University (ZJU)in this summer. Previously, he was a visiting student of University of Michigan (UMich)and a research intern of Westlake Institute for Advanced Study (WIAS).
